[2025 | Age 22] [TextBlock(text="Reflecting on my recent trip to Japan and the vibrant fusion of tradition with tech, I'm rethinking my blockchain projects. How can we preserve cultural identity in a decentralized world? Time to get creative with smart contracts and digital identity. Maybe AI can help us find the balance.   ", type='text')]
